No Triple Crown, not being undefeated...

00:00:58.970 --> 00:01:03.140
What am I supposed to run for now?

00:01:21.450 --> 00:01:28.670
Umamusume

00:01:24.620 --> 00:01:28.670
Pretty Derby

00:02:35.020 --> 00:02:37.580
Good morning.

00:02:35.570 --> 00:02:40.550
{\an1}Episode 6
 Searching for a Reason

00:02:46.650 --> 00:02:48.090
You're McQueen's...

00:02:49.490 --> 00:02:51.380
Six months to heal?

00:02:51.380 --> 00:02:56.500
Yes. It's a genuine shame I'll be unable 
to run in the Takarazuka Kinen,

00:02:56.500 --> 00:02:59.990
but for the time being, I'll be recuperating 
at home, away from the school.

00:02:59.990 --> 00:03:02.760
I assume this means you'll be taking 
a break from your team, too.

00:03:02.760 --> 00:03:06.000
Yes. I've made sure to 
get Trainer's approval.

00:03:06.600 --> 00:03:08.890
What has Teio said about it?

00:03:09.790 --> 00:03:15.030
You two are rivals, aren't you? 
You just competed in the Spring Tennoushou.

00:03:15.030 --> 00:03:17.780
The Tennoushou is over now.

00:03:17.780 --> 00:03:22.150
My only concern now is 
what to do in the future.

00:03:22.150 --> 00:03:23.160
I see.

00:03:23.160 --> 00:03:26.780
No horse girl can resist their 
instinct to seek victory.

00:03:28.090 --> 00:03:30.190
If you'll excuse me.

00:03:41.850 --> 00:03:44.590
So... you spoke to Teio, then.

00:03:45.140 --> 00:03:45.970
Yes.

00:03:45.970 --> 00:03:51.210
Though I had thought this type of thing 
would be best conveyed in person...

00:03:51.210 --> 00:03:53.810
No, this saves me the trouble.

00:03:54.250 --> 00:03:56.310
Let's head to our destination, Butler.

00:03:56.310 --> 00:03:58.010
Very good, miss.

00:03:58.740 --> 00:04:00.780
It's a shame about McQueen,

00:04:01.080 --> 00:04:05.500
but Teio's injuries aren't as bad, 
so she'll be able to run again in the fall.

00:04:06.990 --> 00:04:08.950
Come on, why the long faces?

00:04:11.040 --> 00:04:13.080
McQueen's gonna be back, you hear me?

00:04:14.010 --> 00:04:14.810
Yeah.

00:04:14.810 --> 00:04:18.130
Teio is working hard in spite of 
her injuries, so we'd better, too!

00:04:18.130 --> 00:04:19.760
Let's start training!

00:04:19.760 --> 00:04:22.910
Oh yeah! Time for some 
Golshi original special training!

00:04:22.910 --> 00:04:24.490
Let's do it, Teio!

00:04:25.840 --> 00:04:27.120
Teio-san?

00:04:27.760 --> 00:04:31.140
Oh, sorry about that! 
Yeah, let's start training.

00:04:33.640 --> 00:04:35.350
What did you want to talk about?

00:04:35.350 --> 00:04:38.810
I figured I'd run the race
plan for this fall by you.

00:04:38.810 --> 00:04:40.520
Tokai Teio's

00:04:38.810 --> 00:04:40.520
Perfect Return Racing Plan!!

