00:05:05.550 --> 00:05:08.650
It's been a very intense racing season.

00:05:08.650 --> 00:05:11.600
It definitely has, with a lot of drama.

00:05:11.600 --> 00:05:12.720
You got it from here!

00:05:11.600 --> 00:05:14.060
Takarazuka Kinen

00:05:12.030 --> 00:05:13.400
Mejiro Palmer in front! Kania Curation behind her!

00:05:12.720 --> 00:05:14.060
Leave it to me!

00:05:13.400 --> 00:05:14.880
But there's no catching Palmer!

00:05:14.070 --> 00:05:17.040
Because we're BFFs!

00:05:14.880 --> 00:05:15.850
And just now—

00:05:15.850 --> 00:05:17.420
She crosses the goal!

00:05:17.420 --> 00:05:21.150
In McQueen's absence, Palmer has
 won the Takarazuka Kinen!

00:05:17.690 --> 00:05:19.490
I did it, Trainer!

00:05:19.490 --> 00:05:21.150
Huh? Trainer?!

00:05:21.150 --> 00:05:23.900
Today's Special Guest

00:05:21.150 --> 00:05:23.900
The Ultim-Outrunner Horse Girl!

00:05:21.150 --> 00:05:23.900
Mejiro Palmer

00:05:21.730 --> 00:05:23.380
Our guest today is Mejiro Palmer-san,

00:05:23.380 --> 00:05:26.560
who came away with a splendid 
win at the Takarazuka Kinen.

00:05:26.560 --> 00:05:28.740
What are your thoughts now, 
looking back on the race?

00:05:28.740 --> 00:05:30.370
Let's see...

00:05:30.370 --> 00:05:33.730
I think at the Tennoushou, I wasn't prepared 
enough for how much I'd have to run.

00:05:31.040 --> 00:05:32.000
Palmer!

00:05:32.650 --> 00:05:35.020
Palmer, Palmer!

00:05:33.730 --> 00:05:36.460
But during the Takarazuka, 
I could tell Helios was behind me,

00:05:36.460 --> 00:05:38.820
going as hard as she could,

00:05:36.460 --> 00:05:42.670
Mejiro Palmer

00:05:38.820 --> 00:05:41.380
and that made me able to run even more.

00:05:40.100 --> 00:05:42.670
Oh, wow! She mentioned me!

00:05:42.670 --> 00:05:47.300
I think having someone like a rival 
to compete with is really awesome!

00:05:47.300 --> 00:05:48.550
Palmer...

00:05:48.780 --> 00:05:52.170
Now that I've got a BFF... 
no, a running friend,

00:05:52.170 --> 00:05:53.760
I know I can win next time!

00:05:54.430 --> 00:05:56.160
Thank you so much.

00:05:56.730 --> 00:05:59.690
And coming soon is the 
next race in the classics.

