Mihono Bourbon

00:06:22.670 --> 00:06:27.010
The Incline Prodigy

00:06:22.670 --> 00:06:34.970
Umamusume Tariku

00:06:24.250 --> 00:06:26.570
This horse girl's morning starts early.

00:06:27.850 --> 00:06:30.500
She never misses her daily training.

00:06:30.500 --> 00:06:32.710
It's natural that I work hard.

00:06:31.610 --> 00:06:34.970
Onto
an
Undefeated
Triple
Crown...

00:06:32.710 --> 00:06:36.240
And winning is equally natural.

00:06:38.930 --> 00:06:43.690
Aim to be an undefeated Triple Crown horse girl!

00:06:40.470 --> 00:06:42.790
An undefeated Triple Crown, huh?

00:06:49.270 --> 00:06:51.020
I've finally come this far.

00:06:51.820 --> 00:06:54.000
I know you're there, Rice.

00:06:56.950 --> 00:07:00.300
The Triple Crown that even 
Tokai Teio-san was unable to achieve...

00:06:56.990 --> 00:07:00.520
R
i
c
e
S
